{"type":null,"faqId":44122,"title":"超级夜景拍照和普通手机的长时间曝光有什么区别","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">普通手机的长曝光（M档）是纯粹的物理曝光技术拍摄，对手持要求较高，而且由于宽容度限制，容易出现亮处过曝等场景。此外由于传感器以及ISP的限制，曝光时间不会很长，一般手机只能到8秒钟，极少有超过30秒钟。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">而超级夜景使用了更先进的算法技术，通过拍摄多帧合成来获取照片，拍摄时间理论上没有限制，通过支持更长时间曝光，比较黑的场景能够拍出来，甚至人眼看不清的也能拍出来，此外通过算法加强处理，照片效果和降噪效果更好，通过拍摄后重调白平衡等技术来确保可以获得更好的效果。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9622","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400098000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"超级夜景,曝光,单反,B门夜景","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}